item.title: CVE-2021-25068|2024-08-03T19:56:09.944Z -- unknown -- sync%20woocommerce%20product%20feed%20to%20google%20shopping
item.description: The Sync WooCommerce Product feed to Google Shopping WordPress plugin through 1.2.4 uses the 'feed_id' POST parameter which is not properly sanitized for use in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection vulnerability in the admin dashboard
